schemas.name: foaf.graphql
schemas.content:
"""An agent (eg. person, group, software or physical artifact)."""
type Agent implements AgentInterface & RdfsResourceInterface {
  """A unique identifier for the resource."""
  id: ID

  """
  personal mailbox - A  personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated
  with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static
  inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at
  most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.
  """
  mbox: [OwlThing]

  """
  sha1sum of a personal mailbox URI name - The sha1sum of the URI of an Internet
  mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the  first owner of the mailbox.
  """
  mbox_sha1sum: [String]

  """
  The gender of this Agent (typically but not necessarily 'male' or 'female').
  """
  gender: String

  """jabber ID - A jabber ID for something."""
  jabberID: [String]

  """AIM chat ID - An AIM chat ID."""
  aimChatID: [String]

  """Skype ID - A Skype ID."""
  skypeID: [String]

  """ICQ chat ID - An ICQ chat ID."""
  icqChatID: [String]

  """Yahoo chat ID - A Yahoo chat ID."""
  yahooChatID: [String]

  """MSN chat ID - An MSN chat ID."""
  msnChatID: [String]

  """A weblog of some thing (whether person, group, company etc.)."""
  weblog: [Document]

  """An OpenID for an Agent."""
  openid: [Document]

  """
  A tipjar document for this agent, describing means for payment and reward.
  """
  tipjar: [Document]

  """Something that was made by this agent."""
  made: [OwlThing]

  """A page about a topic of interest to this person."""
  interest: [Document]

  """A thing of interest to this person."""
  topic_interest: [OwlThing]

  """Indicates an account held by this agent."""
  account: [OnlineAccount]

  """account - Indicates an account held by this agent."""
  holdsAccount: [OnlineAccount]

  """
  The birthday of this Agent, represented in mm-dd string form, eg. '12-31'.
  """
  birthday: String

  """The age in years of some agent."""
  age: String

  """
  A string expressing what the user is happy for the general public (normally) to know about their current activity.
  """
  status: [String]

  """The subject is an instance of a class."""
  type: [RdfsClass]

  """Idiomatic property used for structured values."""
  value: [RdfsResource]

  """A description of the subject resource."""
  comment: [String]

  """A human-readable name for the subject."""
  label: [String]

  """A name for some thing."""
  name: [String]

  """Further information about the subject resource."""
  seeAlso: [RdfsResource]

  """The defininition of the subject resource."""
  isDefinedBy: [RdfsResource]

  """A member of the subject resource."""
  member: [RdfsResource]

  """
  The property that determines the predicate of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.
  """
  annotatedProperty: [RdfsResource]

  """
  The property that determines the subject of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.
  """
  annotatedSource: [RdfsResource]

  """
  The property that determines the object of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.
  """
  annotatedTarget: [RdfsResource]

  """
  The annotation property that indicates that a given entity has been deprecated.
  """
  deprecated: [RdfsResource]

  """
  The property that determines the collection of members in either a
  owl:AllDifferent, owl:AllDisjointClasses or owl:AllDisjointProperties axiom.
  """
  members: [RdfList]

  """
  The annotation property that provides version information for an ontology or another OWL construct.
  """
  versionInfo: [RdfsResource]
}
